README


Thesis Repository - web-based institutional repository for thesis
Serve to Search, Parse, Submit and Present Thesis in PDF and/or BibTeX files.


Used:

Built on Nodejs web application platform.		   
Expressjs - used as a web application framework
using $npm install - all packages from package.json file are installed
+
Viewerjs installed in /public folder, for files display

Databases: MongoDB - on MongoLab (mongodb hosting service)
				   - or on any other server
		   mongoose - for DB object modeling (included in package.json)

		   
After installation:

run $node server.js
result: app is running on your server(localhost:8080 by default)
	   
Authors: Christian N., Asmir B., Hrvoje H.